query:
SELECT
    latitude,
    longitude,
    mmsi,
    TIMESTAMP AS msgtime,
    course_over_ground,
    navigation_status_id AS navigational_status,
    rate_of_turn,
    speed_over_ground,
    true_heading,
    distance_to_shore
FROM
    ais_positions
WHERE
    mmsi = $1
    AND TIMESTAMP BETWEEN $2 AND $3
    AND $1 NOT IN (
        SELECT
            a.mmsi
        FROM
            ais_vessels a
            LEFT JOIN fiskeridir_vessels f ON a.call_sign = f.call_sign
        WHERE
            a.mmsi = $1
            AND (
                (
                    a.ship_type IS NULL
                    OR a.ship_type = ANY ($4::INT[])
                )
                AND (
                    COALESCE(f.length, a.ship_length) IS NULL
                    OR COALESCE(f.length, a.ship_length) < $5
                )
            )
    )
ORDER BY
    TIMESTAMP ASC
